race.description: Tabtouch - Have You Got The Touch Handicap
race.comment: DIAMOND WARRIOR (3) landed midfield and quickened nicely to finish 1.3L off the winner at Northam first-up. He's sure to be better for that effort and the drop back to 1200m isn't an issue. Looks well placed in this race second-up and from a good gate, he can shed the maiden tag. HASANI (1) made it back-to-back wins last start when a 0.5L victor in Heavy going over 1400m here. That was 42 days ago now and he hasn't been sighted publicly since. This looks like a kick off point with targets further down the road, though he may still be too classy for his rivals. INTOXICATING (7) bumped into a good one first-up at Northam with the winner of that race winning at Ascot on Saturday. Pike hops in the saddle now replacing the apprentice hoop and she can put her best foot forward. SPIRITED STRIKE (2) won well two back and only just missed in a similar race a fortnight ago. Ticks a few boxes. TIGER TANK (5) has claims off a solid debut performance at Kalgoorlie.
